      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's weird. I could have sworn I saw a 15% drop in MRR on the dashboard when I logged in this morning. Are you sure there wasn't some kind of error in the reporting for last month? I'd hate for Sequoia to run their own analysis and see a dip we didn't mention. Can you walk me through exactly how you calculated that 2% churn figure?",
